precis:
PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1995, NO. 8 - which
prohibits the staking of mineral claims on certain parcels of lands in
Mayo and near Haines Junction, Carmacks and Beaver Creek in the Yukon
Territory, which are required for airport purposes.
